---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import portrait from '../assets/lisa-photo.png';
---

<Layout
  title="About — AiCraft"
  description="AiCraft is a micro-consultancy run by a data scientist and designer with deep experience in AI, NLP, and data engineering—built for small organizations."
>
  <!-- Page hero -->
  <section class="page-hero section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1 class="page-hero__title">Senior expertise, small-studio delivery</h1>
      <p class="page-hero__lead">
        I'm a data scientist and designer who has spent a career at the intersection of language,
        data, and human-computer interaction. I now help small organizations turn messy, underused
        information into tools that support real-world decisions.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story -->
  <section class="section story-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-image-slot">
        <Image
          src={portrait}
          alt="Lisa Harper"
          class="about-portrait"
          widths={[400, 640, 800]}
          sizes="(max-width: 860px) 45vw, 280px"
          quality={85}
          loading="eager"
        />
        <blockquote class="about-values">
          <p>
            After retiring from federal service, I live fulltime in Hampshire County, WV — a rural
            community with real needs and a lot of unrealized potential. I volunteer and teach
            locally, and I started AiCraft because I believe AI can be harnessed to help communities
            like mine actually thrive.
          </p>
          <footer class="about-values__byline">Lisa Harper · Hampshire County, WV</footer>
        </blockquote>
      </div>

      <div class="story-inner">
      <div class="story-text">
        <h2 class="story-heading">Background</h2>

        <p>
          Before starting AiCraft, I led interdisciplinary teams in AI, cloud computing, and data
          analytics inside the U.S. intelligence community. I both led applied research programs and the development of enterprise-scale knowledge
          retrieval and language AI systems. That work taught me how to design
          "intelligence-grade" solutions that are both technically solid and usable by people
          working under pressure and real constraints.
        </p>

        <p>
          Earlier in my career, I worked as a principal AI engineer on federally-funded projects
          and industry–academic collaborations, building dialogue systems, interfaces, and
          visualizations for complex datasets. Alongside that applied work, I've taught graduate
          courses in natural language processing (NLP) and human–computer interaction (HCI) — helping students
          build user interfaces with AI under the hood. 
        </p>

        <p>
          At AiCraft, you get that same level of experience, but in a small-studio format: one
          client at a time, clear scopes, and straightforward communication. I work directly with
          you and your team—from the first whiteboard sketch to the live dashboard, AI agent, or
          searchable archive. You own what we build together. I teach you how to use it and make 
          it better over time.
        </p>

        <p>
          Today my focus is on small businesses, local governments, and nonprofits with more data
          than staff time. If your world is spreadsheets, email, historical records, and basic web
          tools, I help you take a measured step into AI, automation, and data apps—starting with
          one concrete problem we can solve together in weeks or months.
        </p>

        <p>
          Every AI feature includes error analysis and evaluation so we can see how it behaves in
          the real world and make it better over time, not worse.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="story-credentials">
        <div class="credentials-block">
          <p class="credentials-label">Areas of depth</p>
          <ul class="credentials-list">
            <li>AI technical program management</li>
            <li>Natural language processing & language AI</li>
            <li>Conversational agents</li>
            <li>Knowledge retrieval & semantic search</li>
            <li>AI evaluation</li>
            <li>Data science & analytics</li>
            <li>Information & interaction design</li>
            <li>Static & JAMstack web development</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="credentials-block">
          <p class="credentials-label">How I work</p>
          <ul class="credentials-list">
            <li>One scheduled engagement at a time—so I can go deep</li>
            <li>Clear scope before any development begins</li>
            <li>Plain language, no mystery</li>
            <li>You own what we build</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </aside>
      </div><!-- /.story-inner -->
    </div><!-- /.container -->
  </section>

  <!-- Case study -->
  <section class="section case-section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Selected work</p>
      <div class="case-card">
        <div class="case-card__label-row">
          <span class="case-card__type">Case study</span>
          <a href="https://cacaponmusicanddance.org" class="case-card__link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            cacaponmusicanddance.org ↗
          </a>
        </div>
        <h2 class="case-card__title">Cacapon Music & Dance Foundation</h2>
        <p class="case-card__context">
          A small nonprofit connecting donors, scholarship students, and local square dance events.
          They needed a modern site that could be hosted for free, was easy for volunteers to
          maintain, and made it simple to share events, newsletters, and forms with their community.
        </p>

        <div class="case-card__body">
          <div class="case-what">
            <p class="case-section-label">What I did</p>
            <ul class="case-list">
              <li>Researched similar music and dance nonprofits to identify best-practice content, structure, and calls to action.</li>
              <li>Developed a clear information architecture and key user task flows ("apply for a scholarship," "donate," "find an event") and reviewed them with the client before implementation.</li>
              <li>Implemented a lightweight, future-proof site using plain HTML hosted via GitHub and Netlify, minimizing maintenance overhead and lock-in.</li>
              <li>Created a concise style guide and decision log so future maintainers—human or AI—can quickly understand how the site and data are organized.</li>
              <li>Applied the existing logo and brand, selecting complementary typography, color, and motion cues to emphasize music, movement, and community.</li>
              <li>Designed a custom events calendar that highlights upcoming dances and deadlines in a way that's easy for families to scan and for volunteers to update.</li>
              <li>Structured pages and content with basic SEO and clear question–answer patterns so both search engines and AI tools can better understand "who we are" and "how to participate."</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="case-outcomes">
            <p class="case-section-label">Outcomes</p>
            <ul class="case-list">
              <li>A fast, low-cost site the organization can update themselves, with clear paths for donors, students, and dancers.</li>
              <li>Centralized events, forms, and newsletters—reducing email back-and-forth and manual updates.</li>
              <li>Better surface area for search and AI-driven question answering, making it easier for people to discover how to get involved.</li>
              <li>After launch: an internal lightweight CRM to track grants, volunteers, and tech requests.</li>
              <li>Reduced future onboarding time by capturing key design and technical decisions in clear, lightweight documentation.</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="case-impact">
              <p class="case-impact__label">Since launch</p>
              <p class="case-impact__text">
                CMDF has acquired additional sponsorship and is now working to expand its programs
                across two more counties—growth made possible in part by a clearer digital presence
                and better-organized donor and event data.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="work-note">
        <p class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">In progress</p>
        <p>
          I'm currently building out internal demo projects—searchable archives, AI coaching agent, and an AI FAQ pilot—that illustrate the kind of work I do for clients. These
          will appear here over time.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section about-cta">
    <div class="container about-cta__inner">
      <h2 class="about-cta__heading">Work with AiCraft</h2>
      <p class="about-cta__body">
        I take on a small, focused engagements, scheduled focus deeply on your need. If you have a data,
        automation, or web problem you'd like to talk through, the best first step is a short
        conversation.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="button button--primary">Get in touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .page-hero__title {
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    line-height: 1.0;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    max-width: 20ch;
  }

  .page-hero__lead {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    max-width: 58ch;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* portrait + values */
  .about-image-slot {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }

  .about-portrait {
    display: block;
    width: 280px;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .about-values {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    align-self: center;
  }

  .about-values::before {
    content: '\201C';
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 5rem;
    line-height: 0.8;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .about-values p {
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 1.8vw, 1.25rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    line-height: 1.55;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .about-values__byline {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
  }

  @media (max-width: 680px) {
    .about-image-slot {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .about-portrait {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 280px;
    }
  }

  /* story */
  .story-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .story-heading {
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.5vw, 1.875rem);
  }

  .story-text p {
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .story-text p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .credentials-block {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .credentials-block:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .credentials-label {
    margin: 0 0 0.875rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.07em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
  }

  .credentials-list {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .credentials-list li {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.5;
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .credentials-list li::before {
    content: '·';
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* case study */
  .case-section {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
  }

  .case-card {
    padding: 2.5rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .case-card__label-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .case-card__type {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
  }

  .case-card__link {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color var(--duration-fast) var(--ease-standard);
    opacity: 1 !important;
  }

  .case-card__link:hover {
    color: var(--color-ink);
    opacity: 1 !important;
  }

  .case-card__title {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
  }

  .case-card__context {
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 66ch;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .case-card__body {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }

  .case-section-label {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.07em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
  }

  .case-list {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.625rem;
  }

  .case-list li {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.6;
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.625rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .case-list li::before {
    content: '—';
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .case-impact {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    background: rgba(217, 170, 82, 0.1);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
  }

  .case-impact__label {
    margin: 0 0 0.375rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.07em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
  }

  .case-impact__text {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .work-note {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px dashed var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .work-note p:last-child {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .about-cta__inner {
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  .about-cta__heading {
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
  }

  .about-cta__body {
    margin: 0 0 1.75rem;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .story-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .case-card__body {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
